<li id="cite_note-3"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Listed by <a href="/wiki/BoxRec" title="BoxRec">BoxRec</a> as southpaw, but regularly <a href="/wiki/Boxing_styles_and_technique#Switch-hitter" title="Boxing styles and technique">switch-hits</a> as an <a href="/wiki/Orthodox_stance" title="Orthodox stance">orthodox</a>.</span>
</li>
